OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774559156
OL,3,CGuernsey's granite imports at highest
OL,4,Cever levels due to quarry problems
OL,6,FGuernsey is importing granite at its
OL,7,Fhighest-ever rate, due to sub-standard
OL,8,Fstone found at Chouet Quarry and
OL,9,Fsoaring demand.
OL,11,FRonez, the construction materials
OL,12,Fwholesaler operating at the quarry,
OL,13,Fsay they are having to import as much
OL,14,Fas 80% of their target production rate.
OL,16,FRonez's business model is based on a
OL,17,Ftarget production rate of 2,000 tonnes
OL,18,Fper week, or around 100,000 tonnes per
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
