CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774559156
OL,3,CGuernsey's granite imports at highest
OL,4,Cever levels due to quarry problems
OL,6,FHowever, Roussell estimates the
OL,7,Fcompany has been importing between
OL,8,F1,000 and 1,600 tonnes every 7 to 14
OL,9,Fdays since January.
OL,11,FThe company has warned that imports
OL,12,Fare likely to continue well into the
OL,13,Fsummer months.
OL,15,FGranite is a key material in the
OL,16,Fconstruction of houses, roads, and
OL,17,Faggregate for drains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774559156
OL,3,CGuernsey's granite imports at highest
OL,4,Cever levels due to quarry problems
OL,6,FBut the stone found at Chouet so far
OL,7,Fhas been accompanied by high rates of
OL,8,Fclay and weathered stone, reducing the
OL,9,Fuseful yield of the granite.
OL,11,FQuarry miners have also found that the
OL,12,Fuseful stone is significantly deeper
OL,13,Funderground than their preliminary
OL,14,Fdigs indicated.
OL,16,FSteve Roussell, Director of Guernsey
OL,17,FRonez, said that aggravating factors,
OL,18,Fsuch as oil price hikes inflated by
OL,19,Fthe conflict in Iran, have contributed
OL,20,Fto high costs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774559156
OL,3,CGuernsey's granite imports at highest
OL,4,Cever levels due to quarry problems
OL,6,F"There's always been a certain amount
OL,7,Fof stone that's imported, which rises
OL,8,Fand falls depending on demand," Steve
OL,9,Fexplained. "Over the last few months,
OL,10,Fdemand for aggregate has been a lot
OL,11,Fhigher than usual.
OL,13,F"Imported stone costs a lot more than
OL,14,Fwhat we dig up here. The price of
OL,15,Fshipping to the island, combined with
OL,16,Fharbour costs, makes it significantly
OL,17,Fmore expensive.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774559156
OL,3,CGuernsey's granite imports at highest
OL,4,Cever levels due to quarry problems
OL,6,F"Keeping the quarry dry following an
OL,7,Fexceptionally wet winter and spring
OL,8,Fmeans we're having to buy extra stone
OL,9,Fto deal with these muddy conditions."
OL,11,FTo combat the local shortage of usable
OL,12,Fgranite, Ronez are planning to open a
OL,13,Fnew digging site on the south side of
OL,14,FChouet Quarry, which yielded better
OL,15,Fquality stone during nearby digs last
OL,16,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
